strings:
<voice_0x01000D66><se_low>Yangus: There! I got it!
The Venus' tear!

<voice_0x01000D67><se_high>Red: Now that is quality!
Oh yes, this is the real deal.
Well, Yangus, you excel yerself!

<voice_0x01000D68><se_low>Yangus: Now 'and over the 'orse 'n' cart like
you promised!
<voice_0x01000D69><se_high>Red: ...I never promised that! I said I'd think about it when you brought me the goods.

<voice_0x01000D6A><se_high>Red: And I've thought about it now,
and I'm still not givin' it back.
You can keep the stone.

<voice_0x01000D6B><se_low>Yangus: Oi! That ain't wot you promised!
That's a pretty low trick, Red!
I'm surprised at ya!

<voice_0x01000D6C><se_high>Red: Promises!? You wanna talk about promises!?
If I remember rightly, you promised me ages ago you'd bring me that stone!

<voice_0x01000D6D><se_low>Yangus: Wot? That was years ago!
You can't dredge up the past like that!

<voice_0x01000D6E><se_high>Red: Well you're in no position to argue!
I ain't sayin' it again!
The 'orse stays wiv me!
<voice_0x01000D6F><se_low>Yangus: ...Yer right. I was outta line before breakin' me promise to you an' all. I ain't surprised yer 'acked off wiv me.

<voice_0x01000D70><se_low>Yangus: But this ain't just about me now.
I can't leave wivout the 'orse! It's for the guv!

<voice_0x01000D71><se_low>Yangus: Look, do wot ya want wiv me...
But, I'm beggin' ya, give the 'orse back!
<voice_0x01000D72>Red: ...Eh!
<voice_0x01000D73>Red: Ooh...

<voice_0x01000D74><se_high>Red: ...Awright, awright! Behave, would ya!?
Stop grov'llin' about on the floor! Be a man!
<voice_0x01000D75><se_low>Yangus: Well...?
<voice_0x01000D76><se_high>Red: I thought I'd 'ave a bit of fun wiv ya, but you've lost it! Have the 'orse! Do wot ya want wiv it!

<voice_0x01000D77><se_high>Red: But I'll be keepin' that Venus' tear.
That's what we agreed, right?

<voice_0x01000D78><se_low>Yangus: Yeah, fair enough.
Thanks, Red.
And...sorry about ev'ryfin'.

<voice_0x01000D79><se_high>Red: ...For cryin' out loud! Pull yerself together!
We're done 'ere, right?
So go on then! Hop it!
